reviews.text: Not as good as before but still worth to go
Very delicious chicken chop, should have tried the cutlet too... will definitely return to eat again.

A very classic place for grabbing Taiwanese food. Quick lunch is very much needed for working days... Be prepared the place is so crowded with many people waiting outside the restaurant for take away.

Anyways food is good and inexpensive. The combination is usually meat plus sausage plus rice. Not a really healthy choice but once in a while it's okay!
its a local hk food restaurant which the pan fried chicken thigh with black pepper is very delicious, worth to try!

A superb place for lunch if your craving Hk-Style grilled chicken with pepper and rice. Service is fast and food was hot and fresh. Would definitely recommend this restaurant to anyone who is a fan of hk style fast food.

result.name: 榮式燒雞扒專門店

reviews.text: 味道不錯😀
餐廳整潔, 食物好味, 雞扒無雪味, 肉醬車厘茄偏酸, 挺開胃
燒雞扒好吃，“雞藕天成”是這店2大招牌菜合二為一，不妨一試。 服務親切，環境整潔但座位較為狹窄。因為即叫即燒時間較為長，但值得一等！
雞扒蓮藕餅……無敵😍

煎雞扒比以前薄，係入味，充滿蜜汁同黑椒，皮無乜。
炸雞扒，炸粉薄但淋左，雞肉都嫩口嘅，但就係淋嘅炸粉皮。
除左飯，仲有粉檬，出前一丁。 
價錢又唔係平。一般
